DarkMouse::

She swallowed hard. "Gulp. Why do I not like the sound of this?"
She stopped and transformed into bot mode and took out her plasma 
piston and kept going. She stayed undercover and moved silently 
through the brush as she made her way to the old Pack lair.

of use to

me I saw

turned into
